            "content_html": "<div class=\"project-text formatted-text container-sm\">\n<p>Key Art for the upcoming horror game Video Ghastlies.</p>\n<div class=\"project-description\">\n<p>Indie Publisher <a href=\"https://www.orointeractive.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ORO Interactive</a> approached me to help them create the key art for the exciting horror title Video Ghastlies. <br>Their pitch was to produce an image evocative of the 80s horror-film VHS covers. Hard to say no to that.</p>\n<p>Beside the main artwork, I also delivered the variations designed to be integrated in Steam.</p>\n</div>\n<figure ><figure class=\"post__image post__image--wide\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/38/hugo-halle-steamstore-assetshowcase-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" srcset=\"https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/38/responsive/hugo-halle-steamstore-assetshowcase-2-xs.jpg 300w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/38/responsive/hugo-halle-steamstore-assetshowcase-2-sm.jpg 480w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/38/responsive/hugo-halle-steamstore-assetshowcase-2-md.jpg 749w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/38/responsive/hugo-halle-steamstore-assetshowcase-2-xl.jpg 1200w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/38/responsive/hugo-halle-steamstore-assetshowcase-2-xxl.jpg 1600w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/38/responsive/hugo-halle-steamstore-assetshowcase-2-xxxl.jpg 2560w\"></figure>\n<figcaption >Steam Page Assets</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p> </p>\n</div>",
