            "content_html": "<div class=\"project-text formatted-text container-sm\">\n<p>Key Art for the Save &amp; Sound online music festival - 2023 edition <br>Used as a base for the edition's visual identity, and every piece of marketing material.</p>\n<p><strong>Save &amp; Sound:</strong> <br>• Steam front page feature <br>• Online music festival over 4 days <br>• Unique content from 70+ video games</p>\n<p>The event is organized by <a href=\"Bedtime.io\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bedtime Digital Games</a>. <br><a href=\"https://www.saveandsound.io/2023\">https://www.saveandsound.io/2023</a></p>\n<figure ><figure class=\"post__image--wide\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/SS23_KeyArt_16x9_2K.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" srcset=\"https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_KeyArt_16x9_2K-xs.jpg 300w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_KeyArt_16x9_2K-sm.jpg 480w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_KeyArt_16x9_2K-md.jpg 749w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_KeyArt_16x9_2K-xl.jpg 1200w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_KeyArt_16x9_2K-xxl.jpg 1600w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_KeyArt_16x9_2K-xxxl.jpg 2560w\"></figure>\n<figcaption >Official Poster</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure ><figure class=\"post__image post__image--wide\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/SS23_AssetShowcase_2k.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" srcset=\"https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_AssetShowcase_2k-xs.jpg 300w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_AssetShowcase_2k-sm.jpg 480w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_AssetShowcase_2k-md.jpg 749w ,https://hugohalle.com/media/posts/18/responsive/SS23_AssetShowcase_2k-xl.jpg 1200w ,https